japan 's lipc to buy beef on april 23 japan 's livestock industri promot corp ( lipc ) said that on april 28 it will import 7,515 tonn of beef for the first half of the 1987 fiscal year start on april 1 under the simultan buy and sell tender system , against 6,813 a year ago . the system call on the agenc to buy beef from trade hou and simultan sell it to user in one tender . the tender quota in april-septemb is 10 pct of the agenc 's beef import share . japan 's beef import quota in 1987/88 wa set at 93,000 tonn against 85,000 for the same period in 1986/87 .